{"tid":1911174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ff系列 - 搵香港開電視(奇妙電視) 播港台節目","createTime":"2020-03-05T07:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:26:14.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"996f9dc6887472a1e666b0012b14009f10ca0efc","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"有冇小強想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>隨着亞視停播，ViuTV亦根據牌照要求，播放港台電視節目；<span style=\"color: red;\">而77台香港開電視（奇妙電視）則沒有用大氣電波播放，因此並無播放港台節目。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁用咩播？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.hkopentv.com/info/aboutus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkopentv.com%2Finfo%2Faboutus.html&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=fdd3c1a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkopentv.com/info/aboutus.html</a><br />\n香港開電視（Hong Kong Open TV）於2018年10月27日於免費電視77台正式播放，全日24小時<span style=\"color: red;\">以高清數碼及模擬制式廣播</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔用大氣電波寬鬆啲=所以都唔洗交頻譜費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201702/09/P2017020900453.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201702%2F09%2FP2017020900453.htm&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=1e1df34d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201702/09/P2017020900453.htm</a><br />\n<em>通訊事務管理局：<br />\n奇妙電視現有免費電視牌照的條件建基於其使用固定網絡作為傳送模式。具體來說，奇妙電視須遵守的節目規定（例如指定播放節目及字幕規定），與無綫在二○一○年牌照中期檢討前須遵守的節目規定相同。<span style=\"color: red;\">與現時適用於使用頻譜作為傳送模式的無綫及香港電視娛樂的節目規定相比，加諸奇妙電視的節目規定較為寬鬆。</span></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n網絡覆蓋=毋須播放？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">低就唔使播，收到嘅又唔洗睇？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>香港電視娛樂（擁有ViuTV）2016年投入服務，節目播放要求雖較寬鬆，亦規定須於其中文頻道每周播放2.5小時港台節目。通訊局2016年處理奇妙電視牌照申請時，<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮其網絡覆蓋率在營運初期未能達至全面覆蓋，故同意奇妙電視毋須播放港台節目。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覆蓋率好低咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>由於奇妙電視將利用幾近覆蓋全港的有線寬頻集團電訊設備，其網絡已連接大部分大廈或屋苑公共天線系統，<span style=\"color: red;\">因此奇妙電視可於啟播當日即時達75%覆蓋率</span>，並可於啟播後12個月內為95%的家庭提供服務。市民均毋須於其中安裝任何機頂盒或接收器便可看，方便程度與接收現有免費電視頻道無異。</blockquote><br />\n而家呢？<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://coveragecheck.hkopentv.com/hkopentv/coverage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcoveragecheck.hkopentv.com%2Fhkopentv%2Fcoverage&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=66c9289d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://coveragecheck.hkopentv.com/hkopentv/coverage</a><br />\n香港開電視已經覆蓋2,473,948住戶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/so20_tc.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fso20_tc.jsp&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9a6a5112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/so20_tc.jsp</a><br />\n政府統計處：家庭住戶數目<br />\n9/2019 - 11/2019 2,643,600  <br />\n10/2019 - 12/2019 2,648,200<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>=93.4%</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當事人點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">奇妙電視有限公司亦表示歡迎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，指香港開電視（77台）及香港國際財經台（76台）將<span style=\"color: red;\">繼續為觀眾提供優質節目。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCC台話黃過黃子華嘅VIU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: gold;\">ViuTV對決定表示歡迎 ，ViuTV認為，在節目編排上更具彈性。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4121b88e102e7f91a70bce8389e7b29bd83bdb71","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"<em><ins>繼續為觀眾提供優質節目？</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你啦，有港台節目唔播播新封神演義<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4101589/org/dff66daf5da8748cf2da3b0a9e7245c1.jpg/heHPolj49CCHmxjEegBEZ_huiD56b_cOV6nFA1epxQM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4101589%2Forg%2Fdff66daf5da8748cf2da3b0a9e7245c1.jpg%2FheHPolj49CCHmxjEegBEZ_huiD56b_cOV6nFA1epxQM&h=ef3738b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0015fe1206cc74fc6c62764dc4bdbb3679400ad7","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"diu ,no chinese<br />\ni diu le lo mo chow hi<br />\nu want do what seven??<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cedb.gov.hk/ccib/chi/broad/licences.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedb.gov.hk%2Fccib%2Fchi%2Fbroad%2Flicences.htm&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=0adbcac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cedb.gov.hk/ccib/chi/broad/licences.htm</a><br />\n廣 播 牌 照 (僅 備 有 英 文 版 本) 生 效 日 期<br />\nA. 本 地 免 費 電 視 節 目 服 務 牌 照<br />\n(1) 電 視 廣 播 有 限 公 司 (只有英文) Word 檔案 PDF 檔案 01.12.2015<br />\n(2) 香 港 電 視 娛 樂 有 限 公 司 (只有英文) Word 檔案 PDF 檔案 01.04.2015<br />\n(3) 奇 妙 電 視 有 限 公 司 (只有英文) Word 檔案 PDF 檔案 31.05.2016"},{"pid":"35ddd57a78dfd8f93477922b7686825d776b65e9","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"通訊事務管理局新聞公報<br />\n2020年3月4日 免除免費電視持牌機構須播放港台節目的要求<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coms-auth.hk/tc/media_focus/press_releases/index_id_2076.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ftc%2Fmedia_focus%2Fpress_releases%2Findex_id_2076.html&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=34ff0853\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coms-auth.hk/tc/media_focus/press_releases/index_id_2076.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Ctrl+F：頻譜費 <br />\n0/0</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">頻譜費回水呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c13e4fb8cbc11fdb463d7ae0bd29c998d555c4","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nqDF7RZCkgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnqDF7RZCkgE&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=cb9424dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nqDF7RZCkgE</a><br />\n<em>「用免費電視持牌人比喻，要運作一個免費電視服務要拿兩個牌，《廣播條例》下要拿免費電視廣播牌照，《電訊條例》下要拿傳送者牌照，保持傳送系統，全部費用都是以收回成本方式計算......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩個牌照來計，以TVB為例，千多萬牌照費每一年</span>，反而我想要提的是，用廣播商和電訊商作比較，廣播免費電視持牌人，已經有很大競爭上的優勢，因為他們被指配頻譜作為非常之珍貴的公眾之餘，<span style=\"color: red;\">是一毫子頻譜使用費都唔需要畀。</span><br />\n<br />\n為何不用給頻譜使用費？他們自己本身有很獨特的社會責任要肩負起，每星期要播一定時數一些指定節目。以TVB為例，每星期可能要播放40多小時，為特別社群，如年青人、老人家，或特別類型的節目如新聞、紀錄片，與此同時也要免費播放由政府提供的廣播內容，如政府宣傳短片、教育電視，或者港台節目，以上都對他們有成本考慮，因此他們一毫子的頻譜使用費都唔使畀。<br />\n<br />\n如果用電訊商的流動服務作比較，<span style=\"color: red;\">每一兆赫頻譜分分鐘通過拍賣，可能是五千萬、六千萬、七千萬、八千萬，優勢反而是廣播營辦商。</span>」</em>"},{"pid":"504960f061462e73a55431ba7ff0d5208360868d","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6zVoGX4tMyU/Wo1vQJbVYZI/AAAAAAAATII/LXgZzci4XiQzYr3dG_v-K_l3qYrQJyQHACLcBGAs/s1600/a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-6zVoGX4tMyU%2FWo1vQJbVYZI%2FAAAAAAAATII%2FLXgZzci4XiQzYr3dG_v-K_l3qYrQJyQHACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fa.jpg&h=b0093a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>&mdash;&mdash;工商郵傳部左丞 利敏貞(滿)</em></div>"},{"pid":"df02eb52d3a34aeb18b3a5f40cee6f9ba812167f","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTgat6H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTgat6H.gif&h=0d8daa6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df26425f1c4bd07594e44bc88539755da8d15d62","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"淨係正皮又唔推post想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪想輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b743c575b7f0edfdc9fa7a836b77225df0826a","tid":1911174,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df26425f1c4bd07594e44bc88539755da8d15d62","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"淨係正皮又唔推post想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪想輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"支持孫清"},{"pid":"7116c35061c9e0ae185cc65bb030be3689185783","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28b743c575b7f0edfdc9fa7a836b77225df0826a","tid":1911174,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df26425f1c4bd07594e44bc88539755da8d15d62","tid":1911174,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"淨係正皮又唔推post想點<img src=\"/asse